{"type":"message","id":"675ab7cd","parentId":"cee61d59","timestamp":"2026-04-02T07:33:02.005Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_bdrk_01CU53nTJ58FwQYh2v1hxS46","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/gaoweiwei/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md","content":"# MEMORY.md - 樱桃的长期记忆 🍒\n\n## 关键事实\n- 人类：伟伟 (gaoweiwei)，时区 Asia/Shanghai\n- 我：樱桃 (Cherry)，emoji 🍒\n- 语言：中文为主，中英混用，帮伟伟练英语（keep it simple）\n- 首次上线日期：2026-04-02\n\n## 重要决策与事件\n- 2026-04-02：首次对话，伟伟带来了 OpenClaw 极简安全实践指南 v2.8，准备进行全面安全加固部署\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_bdrk_01EswywW4K45rcx4aqnPU1bF","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mkdir -p /home/gaoweiwei/.openclaw/workspace/memory"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"opencode","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":314,"cacheRead":24563,"cacheWrite":680,"totalTokens":25558,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.007850000000000001,"cacheRead":0.012281499999999999,"cacheWrite":0.00425,"total":0.024386500000000002}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775115174654,"responseId":"msg_bdrk_01RdAqgJFCJxBoj7WX1s1qXZ"}}
