{"type":"message","id":"5697ccf8","parentId":"501a598d","timestamp":"2026-04-02T07:33:15.883Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"嗯，看起来 exec 工具遇到了问题——Gateway 报 \"pairing required\"。这意味着我目前**没法执行 shell 命令**。\n\n伟伟，在我开始落地安全指南之前，有个障碍需要先解决：\n\n## ⚠️ Gateway 配对问题\n\n我尝试执行命令时收到了 `pairing required` 错误。这意味着 Gateway 还没完成设备配对，我暂时无法：\n- 运行 `chmod`、`sha256sum` 等命令\n- 创建和执行巡检脚本\n- 注册 cron job\n\n**你能帮我检查一下吗？** 试试在终端运行：\n\n```bash\nopenclaw status\n```\n\n或者：\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway status\n```\n\n看看输出是什么，贴给我，我来帮你排查。\n\n---\n\n> 💡 **English tip:** When something blocks your work, you can say: *\"There's a blocker — I need to fix this first before moving on.\"* \n> blocker = 阻碍你继续工作的问题 🚧\n\n一旦 Gateway 配对搞定，我就立刻按照指南的 5 个 Step 开始部署！🍒"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"opencode","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":354,"cacheRead":25243,"cacheWrite":492,"totalTokens":26090,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.00885,"cacheRead":0.012621499999999999,"cacheWrite":0.003075,"total":0.0245515}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775115182092,"responseId":"msg_bdrk_0114nXwWfXmx3CjiMPaAqsvZ"}}
