{"type":"message","id":"ff8b8b1e","parentId":"22612eb3","timestamp":"2026-04-02T07:34:03.766Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\n谢谢伟伟！从截图来看：\n\n- **Gateway 在运行**，session 正常（`agent:main:main`，就是我们现在的对话）\n- **Channels 是空的** — 这说明还没配置任何消息频道（Telegram/Discord 等）\n- 有个 **WARN** 关于 `denyCommands` 配置，不影响核心功能\n\n那 `pairing required` 的问题可能是 exec 工具的权限配置。让我再试一下简单命令："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_bdrk_012cZ6gP3QhSkwhftevcXp27","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"hello from cherry\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"opencode","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":3,"output":207,"cacheRead":25735,"cacheWrite":1967,"totalTokens":27912,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.005175,"cacheRead":0.012867499999999999,"cacheWrite":0.01229375,"total":0.030351249999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775115232843,"responseId":"msg_bdrk_01FTqoVVkvgboFj3nnBZWSx1"}}
