{"type":"message","id":"22f111e2","parentId":"1dc71f8f","timestamp":"2026-04-02T07:36:49.701Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"找到问题了！🎯\n\n截图里能看到：\n\n- **Pending (1)** — 有一个设备配对请求在等批准，标记了 `repair` flag\n- 它的 Scopes 包含 `operator.approvals`、`operator.admin`、`operator.read`、`operator.write` 等全套权限\n- **gateway.auth.mode = token**\n\n这就是我的 exec 被拒的原因——我这个 agent session 对应的设备还在 Pending 状态，没被批准。\n\n**请帮我批准这个 pending 的配对请求：**\n\n```bash\nopenclaw devices approve --latest\n```\n\n批准后我就能执行命令了，然后立刻开始安全指南的部署工作！🍒\n\n> 💡 **English tip:** *\"Approve the pending request\"* = 批准待处理的请求。*Pending* 这个词很常用，意思是\"等待中的、未决的\"（比如 pending order = 待处理订单）。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"opencode","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":3,"output":285,"cacheRead":25735,"cacheWrite":4882,"totalTokens":30905,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.007125,"cacheRead":0.012867499999999999,"cacheWrite":0.0305125,"total":0.050519999999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775115392029,"responseId":"msg_bdrk_01GuTvD22szRD3jeZT4a9SCt"}}
