{"type":"message","id":"c0d35a9e","parentId":"5cf3966a","timestamp":"2026-04-02T07:37:36.854Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"看起来需要你批准我执行命令。这是 OpenClaw 的安全审批机制——每个 exec 命令都需要你确认。\n\n你在界面上应该看到了审批提示，点击 **approve** 就行。\n\n如果你希望以后我的命令不用逐条批准，可以选 **allow-always**（对这类命令永久放行）。不过按照安全指南的精神，**allow-once**（逐条确认）其实更稳妥 😄\n\n> 💡 **English tip:** *\"Allow once\"* vs *\"Allow always\"* — once = 一次，always = 总是。安全领域常说 *\"principle of least privilege\"*（最小权限原则），意思是只给刚好够用的权限。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"opencode","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":220,"cacheRead":29426,"cacheWrite":237,"totalTokens":29884,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.0055000000000000005,"cacheRead":0.014712999999999999,"cacheWrite":0.0014812500000000001,"total":0.02169925}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775115448602,"responseId":"msg_bdrk_017stbpHKD4epPk9q5GX9WcK"}}
