{"type":"message","id":"7a659a16","parentId":"c817a9e3","timestamp":"2026-04-02T07:37:49.650Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_bdrk_01UV77XHbtWFQLKxr9w8bTWG","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Approval required (id d0fe46ec, full d0fe46ec-a480-4de0-af30-ee7f5d163e8c).\nHost: gateway\nCWD: /home/gaoweiwei/.openclaw/workspace\nCommand:\n```sh\necho \"=== OC State Dir ===\" && echo \"${OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR:-$HOME/.openclaw}\" && echo \"=== openclaw.json exists? ===\" && ls -la \"$HOME/.openclaw/openclaw.json\" 2>&1 && echo \"=== paired.json exists? ===\" && ls -la \"$HOME/.openclaw/devices/paired.json\" 2>&1 && echo \"=== Current permissions ===\" && stat -c '%a %U %n' \"$HOME/.openclaw/openclaw.json\" \"$HOME/.openclaw/devices/paired.json\" 2>&1 && echo \"=== OpenClaw version ===\" && openclaw --version 2>&1 && echo \"=== Git in OC dir? ===\" && (cd \"$HOME/.openclaw\" && git remote -v 2>&1 || echo \"No git repo\")\n```\nMode: foreground (interactive approvals available).\nBackground mode requires pre-approved policy (allow-always or ask=off).\nReply with: /approve d0fe46ec allow-once|allow-always|deny\nIf the short code is ambiguous, use the full id in /approve."}],"details":{"status":"approval-pending","approvalId":"d0fe46ec-a480-4de0-af30-ee7f5d163e8c","approvalSlug":"d0fe46ec","expiresAtMs":1775117269644,"host":"gateway","command":"echo \"=== OC State Dir ===\" && echo \"${OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR:-$HOME/.openclaw}\" && echo \"=== openclaw.json exists? ===\" && ls -la \"$HOME/.openclaw/openclaw.json\" 2>&1 && echo \"=== paired.json exists? ===\" && ls -la \"$HOME/.openclaw/devices/paired.json\" 2>&1 && echo \"=== Current permissions ===\" && stat -c '%a %U %n' \"$HOME/.openclaw/openclaw.json\" \"$HOME/.openclaw/devices/paired.json\" 2>&1 && echo \"=== OpenClaw version ===\" && openclaw --version 2>&1 && echo \"=== Git in OC dir? ===\" && (cd \"$HOME/.openclaw\" && git remote -v 2>&1 || echo \"No git repo\")","cwd":"/home/gaoweiwei/.open