{"type":"message","id":"8913b249","parentId":"bd5d9bc5","timestamp":"2026-04-02T07:48:27.088Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_bdrk_01WvzfRZrcrvwVatb59yKGhd","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/cron-help.txt"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"opencode","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":3,"output":60,"cacheRead":65631,"cacheWrite":156,"totalTokens":65850,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.0015,"cacheRead":0.0328155,"cacheWrite":0.0009750000000000001,"total":0.0353055}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775116102597,"responseId":"msg_bdrk_01H6BrSpSSszaFeonELioPHt"}}
{"type":"message","id":"850617af","parentId":"8913b249","timestamp":"2026-04-02T07:48:27.112Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_bdrk_01WvzfRZrcrvwVatb59yKGhd","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n🦞 OpenClaw 2026.4.1 (da64a97) — The only crab in your contacts you actually want to hear from. 🦞\n\nUsage: openclaw cron add|create [options]\n\nAdd a cron job\n\nOptions:\n  --account <id>         Channel account id for delivery (multi-account setups)\n  --agent <id>           Agent id for this job\n  --announce             Announce summary to a chat (subagent-style) (default:\n                         false)\n  --at <when>            Run once at time (ISO with offset, or +duration). Use\n                         --tz for offset-less datetimes\n  --best-effort-deliver  Do not fail the job if delivery fails (default: false)\n  --channel <channel>    Delivery channel (last|<channel-id>) (default: \"last\")\n  --cron <expr>          Cron expression (5-field or 6-field with seconds)\n  --delete-after-run     Delete one-shot job after it succeeds (default: false)\n  --deliver              Deprecated (use --announce). Announces a summary to a\n                         chat.\n  --description <text>   Optional description\n  --disabled             Create job disabled (default: false)\n  --every <duration>     Run every duration (e.g. 10m, 1h)\n  --exact                Disable cron staggering (set stagger to 0) (default:\n                         false)\n  --expect-final         Wait for final response (agent) (default: false)\n  -h, --help             Display help for command\n  --json                 Output JSON (default: false)\n  --keep-after-run       Keep one-shot job after it succeeds (default: false)\n  --light-context        Use lightweight bootstrap context for agent jobs\n                         (default: false)\n  --message <text>       Agent message payload\n  --model <model>        Model override for agent jobs (provider/model or alias)\n  --name <name>          Job name\n  --no-deliver           Disable announce delivery and skip main-session summary\n  --session <target>     Session target (main|isolated)\n  --session-key <key>    Session key for job routing (e.g.\n                         agent:my-agent:my-session)\n  --stagger <duration>   Cron stagger window (e.g. 30s, 5m)\n  --system-event <text>  System event payload (main session)\n  --thinking <level>     Thinking level for agent jobs\n                         (off|minimal|low|medium|high|xhigh)\n  --timeout <ms>         Timeout in ms (default: \"30000\")\n  --timeout-seconds <n>  Timeout seconds for agent jobs\n  --to <dest>            Delivery destination (E.164, Telegram chatId, or\n                         Discord channel/user)\n  --token <token>        Gateway token (if required)\n  --tools <csv>          Comma-separated tool allow-list (e.g. exec,read,write)\n  --tz <iana>            Timezone for cron expressions (IANA) (default: \"\")\n  --url <url>            Gateway WebSocket URL (defaults to gateway.remote.url\n                         when configured)\n  --wake <mode>          Wake mode (now|next-heartbeat) (default: \"now\")\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775116107107}}
{"type":"message","id":"e6658156","parentId":"850617af","timestamp":"2026-04-02T07:48:35.272Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"没有位置参数，命令全靠 flags。重新来："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_bdrk_01Et2JjazYziTtAqRpBYqaVE","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw cron add \\\n  --name \"nightly-security-audit\" \\\n  --description \"夜间安全巡检 (Nightly Security Audit)\" \\\n  --cron \"0 3 * * *\" \\\n  --tz \"Asia/Shanghai\" \\\n  --session \"isolated\" \\\n  --light-context \\\n  --no-deliver \\\n  --message \"Execute this command and summarize the output into a concise security report in Chinese. List all 13 items with emoji status (🚨/⚠️/✅). Start with a one-line summary showing critical/warn/ok counts. Command: bash /home/gaoweiwei/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/nightly-security-audit.sh\" \\\n  --timeout-seconds 300 \\\n  --thinking off \\\n  --tools \"exec,read,write\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"opencode","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":274,"cacheRead":65787,"cacheWrite":879,"totalTokens":66941,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.00685,"cacheRead":0.0328935,"cacheWrite":0.00549375,"total":0.04524225}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775116107113,"responseId":"msg_bdrk_016ivi1sENFNjJiUuefPtzg7"}}
