{"type":"message","id":"cbb93886","parentId":"6087b87f","timestamp":"2026-04-02T07:51:30.146Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"同时写今日 memory："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_bdrk_01LC6U9NaiNNVcbA1ycuaDyR","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/gaoweiwei/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-04-02.md","content":"# 2026-04-02 — 樱桃首日上线 🍒\n\n## 身份建立\n- 伟伟给我取名\"樱桃 (Cherry)\"，emoji 🍒\n- 语言：中文为主，中英混用，帮伟伟学英语\n- 更新了 IDENTITY.md、USER.md、MEMORY.md\n\n## 安全加固部署 (指南 v2.8)\n\n### Step 1 ✅ 认知内化\n- 红黄线规则、事前审计协议、业务风控规则写入 AGENTS.md\n\n### Step 2 ✅ 权限收窄\n- `openclaw.json` 和 `paired.json` 已是 600 权限\n- 生成哈希基线: `sha256sum openclaw.json > .config-baseline.sha256`\n\n### Step 3 ✅ 部署夜间巡检\n- 编写巡检脚本 `scripts/nightly-security-audit.sh`（13 项核心指标）\n- 创建已知问题排除清单 `.security-audit-known-issues.json`\n- 首次测试: **0 critical · 3 warn · 12 ok**（3 warn 均为预期：初始化日文件变更多、出站连接误判已修复、Git 灾备未配置）\n- 注册 Cron: `nightly-security-audit`，每天 03:00 Asia/Shanghai，isolated session，no-deliver（本地报告）\n- `sudo chattr +i` 锁定脚本\n\n### 黄线操作记录\n| 时间 | 命令 | 原因 | 结果 |\n|------|------|------|------|\n| ~15:46 | `sudo ss -tlnp/ulnp/tnp` | 巡检脚本测试运行内部调用 | OK |\n| ~15:50 | `openclaw cron add --name nightly-security-audit ...` | 注册夜间巡检定时任务 | OK，nextRun 明天 03:00 |\n| ~15:50 | `sudo chattr +i nightly-security-audit.sh` | 锁定巡检脚本防篡改 | 待确认 |\n\n### Step 4 🔄 Git 灾备\n- 伟伟确认需要配置，等待提供仓库地址\n\n### Step 5 ⏳ 交付验收\n- 待 Step 3 锁定确认 + Step 4 完成后执行\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"opencode","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":794,"cacheRead":75501,"cacheWrite":352,"totalTokens":76648,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.01985,"cacheRead":0.0377505,"cacheWrite":0.0022,"total":0.059805500000000004}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775116268556,"responseId":"msg_bdrk_01Ub9k6f1u4bXc8iwvqYj18j"}}
