{"type":"message","id":"f7e1875e","parentId":"42fde188","timestamp":"2026-04-02T08:14:29.847Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"嗯，等一下。这样会影响我们正常的交互审批流程。Cron isolated session 用的 agent 可能不是 `main`。让我换个思路 — 还原这个文件，改为直接在 cron message 中避免使用 exec tool："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_bdrk_01Dk1JcihdNAo6kWwy1zJS9w","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/gaoweiwei/.openclaw/exec-approvals.json","edits":[{"oldText":"  \"defaults\": {\n    \"security\": \"allowlist\",\n    \"ask\": \"on-miss\",\n    \"askFallback\": \"deny\"\n  },\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"main\": {\n      \"security\": \"allowlist\",\n      \"ask\": \"on-miss\",\n      \"askFallback\": \"allowlist\",\n      \"allowlist\": [\n        {\n          \"pattern\": \"/usr/bin/bash\",\n          \"lastUsedCommand\": \"bash /home/gaoweiwei/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/nightly-security-audit.sh\"\n        }\n      ]\n    }\n  }","newText":"  \"defaults\": {\n    \"security\": \"allowlist\",\n    \"ask\": \"on-miss\",\n    \"askFallback\": \"allowlist\"\n  },\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"main\": {\n      \"security\": \"allowlist\",\n      \"ask\": \"on-miss\",\n      \"askFallback\": \"allowlist\",\n      \"allowlist\": [\n        {\n          \"pattern\": \"/usr/bin/bash\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"pattern\": \"/usr/bin/ss\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"pattern\": \"/usr/bin/find\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"pattern\": \"/usr/bin/sha256sum\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"pattern\": \"/usr/bin/stat\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"pattern\": \"/usr/bin/grep\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"pattern\": \"/usr/bin/git\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"pattern\": \"/usr/bin/last\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"pattern\": \"/usr/bin/df\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"pattern\": \"/usr/bin/ps\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"pattern\": \"/usr/bin/pgrep\"\n        }\n      ]\n    }\n  }"}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"opencod