{"type":"message","id":"b650c72f","parentId":"e2b1a21f","timestamp":"2026-04-02T11:26:05.663Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"伟伟，帮我最后跑一次：\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart && sleep 5 && openclaw cron run a6d4eef5-f6fe-4fdb-9ae6-dfd0e21cf432\n```\n\n这次把 `askFallback` 改成了 `full`，意味着当 cron session 找不到人批准时，直接放行。你的主会话不受影响——有 UI 在的时候还是会正常弹审批。\n\n跑完告诉我结果，这应该是真的最后一步了！🍒"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"opencode","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":162,"cacheRead":120897,"cacheWrite":928,"totalTokens":121988,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.00405,"cacheRead":0.060448499999999995,"cacheWrite":0.0058000000000000005,"total":0.07030349999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775129158127,"responseId":"msg_01NCdwDvhjCWeH6jtPW6c1As"}}
